abstract: Those excruciating social encounters where you can't remember someone's name.
description: Most of us have had at least one of those excruciating social encounters where you can't remember someone's name. Just what is your subconscious up to while you frantically try to recall it? Cast includes: Don McKellar, Ron Pardo, Patrice Goodman, Ray Landry, Tony Daniels, Athena Karkanis, Nanci Pach, Kedar, Denise Oliver, Dwayne Hill, Chris Landreth and John R. Dilworth. Music: Daniel Janke Animation direction and layout: Sean Craig
